	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Postquam has absolvi, refert mihi d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1059" cert="high">Christophorus</persName><note type="misc"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1059" cert="high">Christopher Fabri</persName></note>, minister <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l339" cert="high">Neocomensis</placeName>, qui cum suo principe huc venit et his diebus<note type="misc">vorn im Brief vom 31. Dez. 1561</note>, dum hic est princeps, concionaturus est hic, <placeName ref="l378" cert="high">Parisiis</placeName> theologos <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2686" cert="high">Sorbonicos</placeName> disputationem habuisse, an liceat regi parere haeretico, item an non liceat pastoribus monere subditos, ut contra talem regem insurgant atque ipsum regno pellant [Affaire Tanquerel Nov. 1561.]</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="manual">Rex ubi haec cognovit, septem illorum theologorum in vincula coniecit; iudicatum super illis in parlamento, adiudicati sunt, ut publice palinodiam canant, deum et regem pro venia precentur.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc dum illi facere nolunt, in carceribus adhuc detinentur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interea decretum, ut in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2686" cert="high">Sorbona</placeName> ad triennium usque nihil amplius disputetur.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Refert item heri ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l301" cert="high">Lugduno</placeName> venisse nobilem quendam cordatum virum, qui testetur per totam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> templa fidelibus esse concessa et <placeName ref="l378" cert="high">Parisiis</placeName> amplissimas et numerosissimas haberi congregationes.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec quoniam nova sunt, reliquis adiicere volui.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale iterum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Communicabis ista fratri quoque meo <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1453" cert="high">[Wolfgang Haller]</persName>, cui alias nescio an nunc scribere possim.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse fehlt]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
